# ── Model artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Small artifacts (encoder, feat_eng, stage1, cat_encoder, canonicalizer, psi)
# are tracked and ship in the Docker image. The three LARGE artifacts exceed
# GitHub's 100MB per-file limit and are fetched at startup from object storage
# (see models_manifest.json + src/api/model_loader.py), so keep them OUT of git.
models/explainer.pkl
models/calibrator.pkl
models/stage2.pkl
models_backup/
models_old_41/

# ── Migration / scratch backups ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.migration_backup/

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log

# ── Large datasets (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
